#---Output of forces--------------------------------------------#

variable vx  atom x
variable vy  atom y
variable vfx atom fx
variable vfy atom fy

compute molchunk all chunk/atom molecule

fix coreout cores ave/chunk ${dumptime_angle} 1 ${dumptime_angle} molchunk v_vx v_vy v_theta v_vfx v_vfy file ${name}_forces.dat